  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You can expect quality cuisine here starting with an excellent hot and cold buffet breakfast. Return each afternoon to free tea and cake and choose four courses from the à la carte menu for dinner with silver service. Your evening meal is made all the more elegant with songs being played on the piano. On your first night, you'll get a free bottle of wine. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Grand Hotel Miramonti Majestic has over 100 years of history and is an iconic hotel <a data-udi="umb://document/2dcb1a3292da421780aa165d449493a9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2dcb1a3292da421780aa165d449493a9}" title="Cortina D’Ampezzo">Cortina</a>. Located on the outskirts of town, the hotel has a wonderful position with stunning surroundings. A free shuttle is on hand at set times throughout the day to whisk you to the slopes with drop offs at the Faloria lift or Cortina’s high street. </p>
<p>Throughout the hotel you'll find lots of grand rooms. The piano bar is perfect for drinks and a spot of music and we love a game of pool in the games room. Our favourite place has to be the spa - the panoramic indoor heated pool is just what you need after a day skiing. </p>
<p>When it’s time to eat you can look forward to Italian food from the à la carte menu and a great selection of wines, we recommend asking the staff for their recommendations.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 3 hours from Innsbruck airport.</p>]]></description>
