  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Spa with heated indoor pool (free), sauna, sensory showers and relaxation area (first visit is free and subsequent visits are €25 per entry, treatments are payable locally)</li>
<li>Gym</li>
<li>Piano bar</li>
<li>WiFi</li>
<li>Free shuttle bus at set times to the town centre &amp; Faloria area between 8.30am - 1pm, 3pm - 8.15pm &amp; 9.30pm - 10.30pm*</li>
</ul>
<p>*<em> Please note that the free shuttle doesn't stop near the Socrepes ski school meeting point. To get to the ski school meeting point you can take the resort bus from the town centre or a taxi from the hotel (approx. €25 each way, payable locally).</em></p>]]></facilityDescription>
