  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is a great choice if you're after something a bit special. It's got an old-world elegance and charm with staff who go out of their way to make you comfortable. A handy shuttle will take you to Cortina's high street or the ski lift and back at the hotel you can enjoy the sophisticated bar and restaurant or the fab spa.</p>]]></listingDescription>
